x4freetext: At higher energies, energy resolution of the
spectrometer was 0.17 micro-s/m. At lower energies it
was 0.0017 eV at 0.5 eV and 0.00024 eV at 0.02 eV.
Note by compiler: Tables I and II of Nucl.Sci.Eng.8,183
giving the enrichments of the Er and Gd samples do not
list major isotopes Er-170 and Gd-160 as well as minor
isotopes Er-162,164 and Gd-152,154. Therefore the
isotopic compositions given for the various enriched
samples add up to less than 100%.
